title: Stargate Universe Season 1 Complete 1080p Blu-Ray 5.1 EN srt
description:
All twenty episodes from the season one Bluray. There is no season two Bluray, alas.

All are full HD, 1920 x 1080p at 23.976fps, with AAC audio 5.1 and English SRT subtitles.

All video is encoded at an average bitrate of 5000 or 5200kbps except for "Air" which was done at 4200kbps.

I have previously uploaded episodes 1-12. Episode 10 has been re-encoded to give 5.1 audio rather than stereo.

Enjoy and please seed.
